msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You stayin' here at our stable?\n"
"That's nice, but check this out.\n"
"\n"
"Go way out south of here, and you'll \n"
"find a flat hill called <2.se_co>Washa's Bluff<3.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>On that hill, there's this mysterious-\n"
"lookin' platform thingie...<5.pa>\n"
"\n"
"Me and Geggle tried all day to figure out\n"
"what it does, but we're stumped...<6.pa>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>If you want to see the platform thingie, \n"
"go south toward <2.se_co>Washa's Bluff<3.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (long)
#. 5: sound
msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Huh?! An <2.se_co>ancient shrine<3.re_co> thingie\n"
"appeared? Who'da thunk that platform\n"
"thingie was hidin' a mystery like that!<4.pa>\n"
"<5.so>I guess that means I have to solve the\n"
"mystery of the shrine thingie now."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (long)
#. 5: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk03"
msgid ""
"<1.so><2.se_co>Ancient shrine<3.re_co>...<4.pa>\n"
"The mystery deepens...<5.pa>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oooh, I don't have time to be lookin'\n"
"after mountain goats right now...<2.pa>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oooh, I don't have time to be drinkin'\n"
"right now...<2.pa>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>There was this one...<2.se_co>Rito<3.re_co> guy that went\n"
"flying to the south after I told him about\n"
"it.\n"
"He was a big ol' bard with some fancy\n"
"instrument thingie. He probably wanted\n"
"to see the altar thingie himself."
msgstr ""

